Text:
The installer included in this rar is the exact same file from the official site. The keygen is the proggie that is giving warnings of infection, not the main app:

[url]http://www.virustotal.com/file-scan/report.html?id=61c4612bab7043c1c27fdea8eac0b218b9cd948a771ca112b621600013fb22b5-1321973474[/url] 

The main app passes scans with minor warnings. The keygen is what is giving concerns. Run keygen in vmwared sandboxie, if it will run for you that way.

Sorry about that. Didn't realize the url tags are unneeded.

Here's a valid link (hopefully):
